Package com.hyperwallet.android

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HyperwalletAuthenticationTokenListener
    A callback interface to handle the submission of an authentication token or an error message in the case of a failure.
    HyperwalletAuthenticationTokenProvider
    The HyperwalletAuthenticationTokenProvider interface provides the Hyperwallet Android Core SDK with an abstraction to retrieve an authentication token.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Configuration
    Authorized user's session Configuration
    ExceptionMapper
    The ExceptionMapper class provides functionality to convert any checked exception into a HyperwalletException.
    HttpTransaction
    HttpTransaction HTTP transaction service that sends request to Hyperwallet API platforms
    Hyperwallet
    The Hyperwallet class is an Android specific implementation of the Hyperwallet platform User APIs.
